snippet.title: Project Anomaly: Urban Supernatural Investigator Demo
snippet.description:
One thing I've always been really bad at is time management so I kind of wish I could just stay there all day over always having to go back after two time periods. I feel like maybe there was more I could do, but... 

You can find the game here: https://darksciencelabs.itch.io/projectanomaly-pilot

If you would like to further support the channel, be sure to check out Youtube Membership! Joining gets you a cute icon next to your name and an exclusive emote to use: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCr_vdRz1iA9St9wyNhlvm_A/join
You will also get access to exclusive posts in the Community Tab :)

Want more than just videos? Find me elsewhere!:
♥ My website (for reviews, game blogs, and various other articles): https://www.crystal-dreams.us
♥ Twitch (catch me streaming live! Following will let you know everytime I stream too): https://twitch.tv/mizunosakura
♥ Twitter: https://twitter.com/pinkseavillage
♥ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/crystaldreamsblog/
♥ Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/crystaldreamsblog/
♥ Tumblr: https://crystalized-dreams.tumblr.com
♥ If you enjoy my videos and want to support beyond just watching, please consider donating!: https://www.paypal.me/crystaldreams (Or you can use the Support option on my main channel page). All support is appreciated :)

Disclaimer:
Due to the content of this channel, videos may contain content copyrighted by another entity or person.
